Heshbladders are creatures that reside in [[Pearl-on-Foam]]. They are named after Hesh.

==Description==
Heshbladders are pink creatures with bug-like legs and fins. They shoot gas from vents on the lower part of their body. They are known to have Water of Hesh stored in them while alive, which are used in [[Cult of Hesh|Heshian]] rituals.